            <title>[SPR-3281] Provide dependency injection using annotations, ala Guice</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-3281</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I just stumbled on the Google Guice project : &lt;a href=&quot;http://code.google.com/p/google-guice/wiki/SpringComparison&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://code.google.com/p/google-guice/wiki/SpringComparison&lt;/a&gt; .&lt;br/&gt;
