                            <comment id="79926" author="cbeams" created="Wed, 13 Jun 2012 09:05:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Indeed, between &lt;tt&gt;@Autowired&lt;/tt&gt;, component-scanning, et al in Spring 2.5; and with &lt;tt&gt;@Configuration&lt;/tt&gt; / &lt;tt&gt;@Bean&lt;/tt&gt; support in  Spring 3.0 and 3.1, Spring&apos;s annotation-based dependency injection is pretty complete. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
